text:
I'm so sad to give two stars :( the only reason I gave two stars is because some of the staff are really great (: but every time I order food from there they seem to get annoyed if it's over the phone, even sometimes in person. And I feel like something is always wrong with the order. For example, I don't understand how rare and well done can get confused. It's just a bunch of stuff that has added up that gets them a bad review from me. And some of the stuff scares me to know if it was true or not.

To add;
The last order I got they didn't give us a receipt that told us the break down, but If the steak and eggs are really as much as they say on the menu, they charged us 15$ for a simple salad with lettuce, chicken and a poorly sliced tomato. :(
